Required software

    * JDK 1.4.2+
    * Ant 1.5+
    * C compiler. If gcc, version 3.2.1 or higher.
    * GNU tar
    * JDBC compliant database. For instance, postgres

Installing GT 3.9.3

First, download the 3.9.3 all source installer. Create a user named
"globus". As the globus user, run

./install-wsrf /usr/local/globus-3.9.3

You may replace "/usr/local/globus-3.9.3" with whatever directory you
wish to install to.
